steps.name: User is on the OMR Branch hotel page
User login "ajithprakasam@gmail.com" and "Prakasam@77"
User should verify success message after login "Welcome Prakasam"
User search hotel "Tamil Nadu","Chennai","Standard","2024-11-11","2024-11-14","2","2" and "2"
User should verify after search hotel success message "Select Hotel"
User save the last hotel name and hotel price
User select the last hotel and accept the alert
User should verify after select success message "Book Hotel"
User add Guest Details "Mr","Prakasam","Manickam","9600809646" and "ajithprakasam@gmail.com"
User add GST Details "9043592058","Greens Tech OMR Branch" and "Thoraipakkam"
User add Special Request "Valet Parking"
User enter payment details, procced with Card Type "Credit Card"
User should verify after hotel booking success message "Booking is Confirmed" and save the order ID
User should verify same selected Hotel is booked or not
User navigate to My Booking page
User should verify after navigate to My Booking page success message as "Bookings"
User search the Order ID
